<SectionComponent IsPrinterFriendly="_isPrinterFriendly"
									SectionEnum="SectionEnum.NewsFlash">
	<SubTitle>
		<b>Important Message From Leadership</b>
		<br />
		Regarding Gatherings and Services
	</SubTitle>
	<ChildContent>
		<div class="card-body">
			<p class="card-text">
				Shalom Living Messiah Family,
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				First, I would like to say THANK YOU for your prayers and continued financial support of Living Messiah during these historic and challenging days we are walking through. The encouraging messages and words I have received from you have been a BLESSING!
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				I am preparing to resume, in person gatherings for Living Messiah services on May 16th, 2020.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				Our leadership team has spent time over the past several weeks examining, discussing and considering the many different perspectives concerning current events.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				We understand that we may not all have the same view or same approach to the situation around us.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				Regardless of our perspectives of the COVID-19 pandemic, we ask everyone to maintain a heart of love and respect towards each other.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				We have been in continual prayer for guidance and direction for this community. Your safety is always of highest priority. We will continue to update you as necessary.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				<b>By attending services in person you assume all risks involved</b>. We ask you to keep these three guidelines in mind;
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Display mutual respect at all times.</li>
				<li>If you are experiencing any symptoms of allergies or illness please join us for services online.</li>
				<li>Take responsibility for protecting yourself and others by practicing safe and healthy habits.</li>
			</ol>
			<p class="card-text">
				We respect the decision of those that will continue to join us online rather than in person and we encourage you to do so if you or your family members are at high risk.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				We look forward to fellowship with each of you in YHWH’s perfect timing.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				Our community meal following service will not resume at this time. Warm weather is here, bring your water bottle along with any food or drink you may need.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				May the insight we each gain and lessons we learn continue to prepare us for days ahead. May our light bring glory and honor to the King of Kings.
			</p>
			<p class="card-text">
				Blessings,
				<br />Mark Webb
				<br />Servant Leader, Living Messiah Ministries
				<br />Elder, B’ney Yosef North America
			</p>
		</div>
	</ChildContent>

</SectionComponent>

